name: The Spread
description: It has been a difficult time for everyone. People have met with loss and loneliness. Everyone is trying to cope in their own way. Us artists have also found ways to cope with our anxieties and depressions by pouring it all out in our works I guess. But the time that we got also helped us reflect on ourselves, try to think positive and stay focussed. And the best way to do that is to keep working…on ourselves and also on our art :)… HERE’S TO LIFE… WE MUST CONTINUE TO LIVE IT UP!
